                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The accumulated bonus damage is displayed together with an Aquablades icon on the player's buffs UI."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The rate of damage increase is a flat additive 10% of the starting damage of Aquablades , and this 10% rate is not increased by Ability Strength mods; however, since the starting damage is affected by Ability Strength, the accumulated rate of damage increase per thrown blade is still better with higher Strength mod builds."
                }
              },
