                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The speed of the throwing animation is increased while riding Merulina and with Natural Talent ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Has a hidden synergy with the Kompressa where Surging Blades can be shot into Kompressa's bubble clusters before they pop. The bubble grows to about 3m in diameter and pulses damage once per second over 20 seconds (not affected by Ability Duration). Up to ten of these bubbles can be created at a time."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "These bubbles will inherit the current accumulated damage bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Enemies hit by the damage pulses will also increase the current damage bonus, but the damage of each bubble is fixed at the time of its creation; any increased damage bonus will be applied to new bubbles."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This interaction also works with other bubble type powers, including Magnetize or enemy Arctic Eximus bubbles."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Surging Blades",
                  "pageId": 1557437,
                  "revisionId": 2779195,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "With Magnetize, the bubbles may not form properly if there are objects like walls or boxes within range of the spinning blades."
                }
              }
